Description: =====
        Krit-Authentication
        =====
        
        Krit-Authentication is a simple Django app to handle authentication
        
        Quick start
        -----------
        
        1. Add "krit-authentication" to your INSTALLED_APPS setting like this::
        
            INSTALLED_APPS = [
                ...
                'krit-authentication',
            ]
        
        2. Include the polls URLconf in your project urls.py like this::
        
            urlpatterns = [
            # other urls
            url(r"^/", include("krit.authentication.urls", namespace="krit_authentication")),
        ]
        
        3. Run `python manage.py migrate` to create the user profile model.
        
